---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="VortKart® | Commercial Go Kart Manufacturer & Track Design Solutions"
  description="VortKart® is a leading commercial go kart manufacturer offering rental go karts, racing chassis production, and complete go kart track design & turnkey solutions worldwide."
  canonical="https://vortkart.com/"
>
<style>
.hero{position:relative;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;overflow:hidden;padding-top:var(--nav-height)}
.hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:url('/images/duratrak-270/8.jpg') center/cover no-repeat}
.hero-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(105deg,rgba(10,10,10,0.92) 0%,rgba(10,10,10,0.65) 55%,rgba(10,10,10,0.3) 100%)}
.hero-content{position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:680px;padding:80px 0 120px}
.hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:rgba(230,57,0,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(230,57,0,0.3);border-radius:100px;padding:6px 16px 6px 6px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--primary);margin-bottom:24px}
.hero-badge span{background:var(--primary);color:var(--white);border-radius:100px;padding:3px 10px;font-size:11px}
.hero h1{margin-bottom:20px;font-size:clamp(36px,4.5vw,56px);line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-.02em;font-weight:800}
.hero h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--primary)}
.hero-sub{font-size:17px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);max-width:560px;margin-bottom:36px;line-height:1.65}
.hero-actions{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:48px}
.hero-meta{display:flex;gap:48px;flex-wrap:wrap;padding-top:28px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)}
.hero-meta-num{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:36px;font-weight:800;color:var(--white);line-height:1}
.hero-meta-num span{color:var(--primary)}
.hero-meta-label{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-top:4px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em}
.scroll-indicator{position:absolute;bottom:40px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:6px;z-index:2;opacity:.6}
.scroll-dot{width:20px;height:32px;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border-radius:10px;display:flex;justify-content:center;padding-top:6px}
.scroll-dot::before{content:'';width:3px;height:6px;background:var(--primary);border-radius:2px;animation:scrollDown 2s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes scrollDown{0%{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1}100%{transform:translateY(12px);opacity:0}}
.advantage-card{background:var(--dark-3);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:36px;transition:var(--transition);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.advantage-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:var(--primary);transform:scaleX(0);transition:transform var(--transition);transform-origin:left}
.advantage-card:hover{border-color:rgba(230,57,0,0.3);transform:translateY(-6px)}
.advantage-card:hover::before{transform:scaleX(1)}
.advantage-icon{width:56px;height:56px;background:rgba(230,57,0,0.1);border-radius:var(--radius-md);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:24px}
.advantage-icon svg{width:28px;height:28px;color:var(--primary)}
.services-preview{background:var(--dark-2)}
.service-preview-card{position:relative;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:4/3;display:block;text-decoration:none}
.service-preview-card img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;transition:transform .5s ease}
.service-preview-card:hover img{transform:scale(1.06)}
.service-preview-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(0deg,rgba(10,10,10,0.92) 0%,rgba(10,10,10,0.3) 60%,transparent 100%)}
.service-preview-content{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;padding:28px}
.service-tag{display:inline-block;background:var(--primary);color:var(--white);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:3px;margin-bottom:8px}
.service-preview-content h4{font-size:22px;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:6px}
.service-preview-content p{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7)}
.service-arrow{position:absolute;top:24px;right:24px;width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;opacity:0;transform:translate(8px,-8px);transition:var(--transition)}
.service-preview-card:hover .service-arrow{opacity:1;transform:translate(0,0)}
.service-arrow svg{width:16px;height:16px}
.about-preview{background:var(--dark)}
.about-preview-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:center}
.about-img-stack{position:relative;overflow:visible}
.about-img-main{border-radius:var(--radius-xl);overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:4/5}
.about-img-main img,.about-img-accent img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.about-img-accent{position:absolute;bottom:-20px;right:-16px;width:52%;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.45),0 0 0 4px var(--dark);aspect-ratio:1;z-index:2}
.about-years-badge{position:absolute;top:32px;left:-20px;background:var(--primary);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:16px 20px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(230,57,0,0.4)}
.about-years-badge .num{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:48px;font-weight:800;color:var(--white);line-height:1}
.about-years-badge .txt{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7)}
.check-item{display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:16px}
.check-icon{width:22px;height:22px;background:rgba(230,57,0,0.1);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.check-icon svg{width:12px;height:12px;color:var(--primary)}
.check-item p{font-size:15px;color:var(--gray-4);margin:0}
.testimonials-section{background:var(--dark-2)}
.testimonials-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px}
@media(max-width:768px){.hero{min-height:auto;padding-bottom:40px}.hero-content{padding:40px 0 80px!important;max-width:100%!important}.about-preview-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr!important;gap:48px!important}.testimonials-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr!important}}
</style>
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div><div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="container"><div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge"><span>Trusted Worldwide</span>Commercial Karting Leader Since 2009</div>
    <h1>Built for <em>Speed.</em><br>Engineered to<br>Last.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">VortKart® manufactures world-class commercial go karts, racing chassis, and delivers complete turnkey karting solutions from track design to opening day.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" style="width:18px;height:18px;vertical-align:-3px;margin-right:8px"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 013.07 11.5 19.79 19.79 0 010 2.94 2 2 0 012 .76h3a2 2 0 012 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L6.09 8.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0122 16.92z"/></svg>Request a Quote</a>
      <a href="/listings" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" style="width:18px;height:18px;vertical-align:-3px;margin-right:8px"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><polyline points="8 21 12 17 16 21"/></svg>View Portfolio</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="hero-meta-item"><div class="hero-meta-num"><span>500</span>+</div><div class="hero-meta-label">Karts Deployed</div></div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item"><div class="hero-meta-num"><span>60</span>+</div><div class="hero-meta-label">Countries Served</div></div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item"><div class="hero-meta-num"><span>15</span>+</div><div class="hero-meta-label">Years Experience</div></div>
    </div>
  </div></div>
  <div class="scroll-indicator"><div class="scroll-dot"></div><span>Scroll</span></div>
</section>
<div class="trust-bar"><div class="container"><div class="trust-bar-inner">
  <div class="trust-item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg><span><strong>ISO 9001</strong> Certified Manufacturing</span></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg><span><strong>48hr</strong> Quote Turnaround</span></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/></svg><span><strong>500+</strong> Happy Clients Globally</span></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"/></svg><span><strong>60+</strong> Countries Served</span></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg><span><strong>5-Star</strong> Rated by Operators</span></div>
</div></div></div>
<section class="section"><div class="container">
  <div class="section-header center fade-in"><div class="label">Why VortKart®</div><h2>The <span class="highlight">Competitive</span><br>Edge You Deserve</h2><p>From factory floor to finish line, VortKart® delivers unmatched quality, performance, and business support at every stage.</p></div>
  <div class="grid-3">
    <div class="advantage-card fade-in delay-1"><div class="advantage-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg></div><h3>Factory-Direct Quality</h3><p>We own and control the entire manufacturing process ensuring consistent quality and competitive pricing with no middlemen.</p></div>
    <div class="advantage-card fade-in delay-2"><div class="advantage-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 010 14.14M4.93 4.93a10 10 0 000 14.14"/></svg></div><h3>Turnkey Track Solutions</h3><p>From concept to grand opening, we design, supply, and commission complete karting attractions. One partner, zero headaches.</p></div>
    <div class="advantage-card fade-in delay-3"><div class="advantage-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg></div><h3>Proven ROI Performance</h3><p>Our commercial karts are engineered for maximum uptime, minimal maintenance cost, and high-throughput operation.</p></div>
  </div>
</div></section>
<div class="stats-strip"><div class="container"><div class="stats-grid">
  <div class="text-center fade-in"><div class="stat-num" data-count="500" data-suffix="+">500+</div><div class="stat-label">Karts Manufactured</div></div>
  <div class="text-center fade-in delay-1"><div class="stat-num" data-count="60" data-suffix="+">60+</div><div class="stat-label">Countries Reached</div></div>
  <div class="text-center fade-in delay-2"><div class="stat-num" data-count="15" data-suffix="+">15+</div><div class="stat-label">Years in Industry</div></div>
  <div class="text-center fade-in delay-3"><div class="stat-num" data-count="98" data-suffix="%">98%</div><div class="stat-label">Client Satisfaction</div></div>
</div></div></div>
<section class="section services-preview"><div class="container">
  <div class="section-header fade-in"><div class="label">What We Do</div><h2>Complete Karting<br><span class="highlight">Solutions</span></h2><p>From a single rental kart to a full-scale attraction — we build it, design it, and deliver it ready to run.</p></div>
  <div class="grid-3">
    <a href="/services#commercial" class="service-preview-card fade-in delay-1"><img src="/images/ev-pro-48/1.jpg" alt="Commercial go karts" loading="lazy" /><div class="service-preview-overlay"></div><div class="service-preview-content"><span class="service-tag">Manufacturing</span><h4>Commercial Go Karts</h4><p>Electric &amp; gas rental karts for all venues</p></div><div class="service-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div></a>
    <a href="/services#racing" class="service-preview-card fade-in delay-2"><img src="/images/proframe-r32/1.jpg" alt="Racing kart chassis" loading="lazy" /><div class="service-preview-overlay"></div><div class="service-preview-content"><span class="service-tag">Performance</span><h4>Racing Kart Chassis</h4><p>Competition-grade tubular steel frames</p></div><div class="service-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div></a>
    <a href="/services#track" class="service-preview-card fade-in delay-3"><img src="/images/proframe-r32/4.jpg" alt="Track design" loading="lazy" /><div class="service-preview-overlay"></div><div class="service-preview-content"><span class="service-tag">Turnkey</span><h4>Track Design &amp; Build</h4><p>Complete attraction from concept to opening</p></div><div class="service-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div></a>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center mt-32 fade-in"><a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Explore All Services</a></div>
</div></section>
<section class="section testimonials-section"><div class="container">
  <div class="section-header center fade-in"><div class="label">Client Voices</div><h2>What Our <span class="highlight">Operators</span> Say</h2><p>Real feedback from track owners, resort managers, and FEC operators who chose VortKart®.</p></div>
  <div class="testimonials-grid">
    <div class="testimonial-card fade-in delay-1"><div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div><p>"VortKart® designed our entire 800m track from scratch, supplied 30 electric karts, and had us operational in under 6 months. The ROI exceeded our projections in year one."</p><div class="testimonial-author"><div class="author-avatar">JM</div><div><div class="author-name">James Mitchell</div><div class="author-title">Owner, SpeedZone Family Park, USA</div></div></div></div>
    <div class="testimonial-card fade-in delay-2"><div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div><p>"We ordered 20 rental karts for our resort's entertainment hub. The build quality is exceptional — two seasons in and maintenance costs are a fraction of what we budgeted."</p><div class="testimonial-author"><div class="author-avatar">SR</div><div><div class="author-name">Sofia Reyes</div><div class="author-title">GM, Grand Marina Resort, Spain</div></div></div></div>
    <div class="testimonial-card fade-in delay-3"><div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div><p>"As a distributor covering Southeast Asia, VortKart® has been our go-to source for 6 years. Their competitive pricing and consistent quality keeps our clients coming back."</p><div class="testimonial-author"><div class="author-avatar">KT</div><div><div class="author-name">Kevin Tan</div><div class="author-title">Director, AsiaPac Amusements, Singapore</div></div></div></div>
  </div>
</div></section>
<section class="section about-preview"><div class="container"><div class="about-preview-grid">
  <div class="about-img-stack fade-in">
    <div class="about-img-main"><img src="/images/ev-pro-48/2.jpg" alt="VortKart facility" loading="lazy" /></div>
    <div class="about-img-accent"><img src="/images/proframe-r32/3.jpg" alt="Kart chassis" loading="lazy" /></div>
    <div class="about-years-badge"><div class="num">15</div><div class="txt">Years of<br>Excellence</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-text fade-in delay-2">
    <div class="label">About VortKart®</div>
    <h2>We Don't Just Build<br><span class="highlight">Karts.</span> We Build<br>Businesses.</h2>
    <p style="margin-top:20px">Founded in 2009, VortKart® has grown from a regional kart fabricator to a globally recognized commercial karting solution provider trusted by operators across 60+ countries.</p>
    <ul class="checklist" style="margin:24px 0 32px">
      <li class="check-item"><div class="check-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div><p>Factory-direct manufacturing — best price guaranteed</p></li>
      <li class="check-item"><div class="check-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div><p>Dedicated project engineers for every turnkey installation</p></li>
      <li class="check-item"><div class="check-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div><p>24/7 technical support and spare parts supply globally</p></li>
      <li class="check-item"><div class="check-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div><p>Custom livery, branding, and fleet configurations available</p></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary">Our Full Story</a>
  </div>
</div></div></section>
<section class="cta-section"><div class="container"><div class="fade-in">
  <div class="label" style="justify-content:center">Start Your Project</div>
  <h2>Ready to Launch Your<br><span class="highlight">Karting Attraction?</span></h2>
  <p>Tell us your vision. We will build it — from a single kart to a full turnkey track.</p>
  <div class="cta-buttons"><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get a Free Quote</a><a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Explore Services</a></div>
</div></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
